{"parse":{"title":"watchdog timer","pageid":4525983,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n{{wp}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# {{lb|en|computer hardware}} An [[electronic]] or [[software]] [[timer]] used to [[detect]] and [[recover]] from [[computer]] [[malfunction]]s by generating a [[timeout]] [[signal]] if it is not periodically reset by the system.\n\n====See also====\n{{col|en|kick|qq1=noun, sense 5, the act of restarting or resetting a watchdog timer}}\n\n{{C|en|Computing}}"}}